revisionDesc.change: 2010-10-25 Piotr Bański: Conversion of TEI P4 source into P5 via tools/freedict_P4toP5.xsl; manual clean-up. We are back to version from before Michael Bunk's re-import from Ergane of 2006-12-21 that was rolled back due to Ergane's cryptic change of database licensing. Renamed "Gaelic" (there is no "Gaelic" as such, other than a language family) to "Scottish Gaelic". Renamed the database from "sco-deu" to "gla-deu".
2005-07-19 Michael BunkFollowing Debian Bug#318025, retitled the dictionary from 'Scottish-German' to 'Gaelic-German'.
